{
  "message": "test(fnp-python): expand axis_out_of_bounds_error_surface_probe to 16 functions\n\nExtended the AxisError regression probe from 6 to 16 axis-taking\nfunctions: prod, std, var, argmax, argmin, cumsum, cumprod, any, all,\nroll added to the existing sum/mean/flip/squeeze/expand_dims/count_nonzero\nset. All 16 now raise AxisError (not plain ValueError) on out-of-bounds\naxis, matching numpy verbatim.\n\nLocks the contract: any new or modified axis-taking function that\nregresses to flat ValueError via map_ufunc_error will trip this probe.",
